## Investigation Queries

### Failed SSH Attempts

```spl
index=linux sourcetype=linux_auth "Failed password"
```

### Successful SSH Logins

```spl
index=linux sourcetype=linux_auth "Accepted password"
```

### Source IP Analysis

```spl
index=linux sourcetype=linux_auth
| rex "from (?<src_ip>\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)"
| stats count by src_ip
| sort -count
```

